Zazler,is,a,backend,as,a,service,for,web,and,mobile,applications,Zazler,offers,features,such,as,accessing,multiple,databases,in,one,interface,specifying,data,queries,and,other,backend,features,The,Zazler,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Zazler,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,posting,data,retrieving,data,and,managing,account,information